Name: Jenel Klein
Text: First time here due to being new to the area I did a lot of research on trying to find something near home and with good quality. My technician was Danny and my nails came out AMAZING!!! I definitely recommend! Danny was fantastic I showed him my inspo picture and he did it perfectly!

Name: Shay Ibraimi
Text: I’ve been coming here for over a year now. Danny always does a great job, he’s fast and efficient and my nails hold up strong for 2-3 weeks without chipping. Great prices, and great quality!

Name: Britt Gaule
Text: Very impressed with this salon as I was half hour late tonight and they still took me and did not rush. thank you and merry Christmas
